message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper involves the use of convolutional neural networks for medical image segmentation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the paper specifically focuses on left atrial segmentation in cardiac images, which is a medical application (cs.MED). Finally, the use of neural networks for medical image segmentation is a topic of interest in the neuroscience community (cs.NEURON).
